2. Fenced Code can then add syntax highlighting
>>>In the Fenced Block, add an optional language identifier to run it through syntax highlighting
>>>>>>They use "Linguist" to perform language detection & syntax highlighting

## Example:

```java
public class HelloWorld
{
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		System.out.println("Hello World!");
	}
}
```
